title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) growth rate in Oman 2024
yAxis: GDP growth compared to previous year
summary: Overall GDP growth compared to previous year has decreased over the Year.
GDP growth compared to previous year is roughly constant from 2016 to 2019, and lastly slightly increasing from 2019 to 2020.

The line drastically remained stable by 14.0 times from Year 2016 to 2017,remained stable by 5.0 times from Year 2017 to 2018,remained stable by 44.0 times from Year 2018 to 2019, and lastly, increased by 92.0 times from Year 2019 to 2020.
Maximum GDP growth compared to previous year, about 4.9 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum GDP growth compared to previous year about 0.04 was reached at Year 2019
